  • Constructor Details

    • Box

      public Box​(StateBox state, int x, int y, int life, Element element)
      Instantiates a new Box. This box is used in Matrice. In a box, we can find some attributes who are useful to run the algorithm of game.
      Parameters:
      state - the state : this attribute can be burned, intact, etc ... this attribute is useful to know if the box can burn again or not ...
      x - the x : coordonate in the matrice (line)
      y - the y : coordonate in the matrice (column)
      life - the life : int between 0 and 100, this attribute will decrease if the box burn.
      element - the element : Tree, rock, vegetation : inform about Color, type etc.
